Enums Class Reference

#include <Shuttle.h>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

Enums is a helper class for Shuttle. It defines enumerations which are used in effects dialogs, in the effects themselves and in preferences.

(If it grows big, we will move it out of shuttle.h).
